data.description: Move right into this Marysville ranch home, located on a quiet cul de sac street close to all the schools.  This 3 bedroom home has lots to offer.  Open kitchen, dining and living rooms with vaulted ceilings and lots of natural light.  Updates include newer furnace, front window , flooring, and roof.  Full finished basement has large family room, flex room, and storage room with built in shelfs.  Outback has spacious deck looking over large fenced back yard.  Kitchen appliances included  Vacant Immediate possession!!
